quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,"“Kodi Ine sindidakuchenjezeni, inu ana a Adamu, kuti musamagwadire Satana, chifukwa iyeyu ndi mdani wanu woonekeratu?”"
  36,61,“Ndi kuti muzindipembedza Ine? Ndithudi imeneyo ndiyo njira yoyenera.”
  36,62,Koma iye adasocheretsa anthu ambiri. Kodi mudalibe nzeru
  36,63,Imeneyi ndiyo Gahena imene munali kulonjezedwa
  36,64,"Lowani m’menemo tsiku lalero ngati chilango, chifukwa chakusakhulupirira kwanu"
  36,65,"Lero, Ife titseka pakamwa pawo, ndipo manja awo ndi amene ayankhule ndi Ife ndiponso miyendo yawo ichitira umboni pa ntchito zoipa zimene anali kuchita"
  36,66,"Chikadakhala cholinga chathu, tikadawachititsa khungu kuti azivutika poyenda. Nanga akadaona bwanji machimo awo"
  36,67,"Chikadakhala cholinga chathu, tikadawasintha kuti asanduke china chake pamalo pamene adaimirira, kuti asapite patsogolo kapena kubwerera m’mbuyo"
  36,68,"Aliyense amene timamukalambitsa, timam’bwezera ku ubwana. Kodi iwo sangazindikire chimenechi"
  36,69,Ife sitidamuphunzitse iye ndakatulo ayi ndiponso si koyenera kuti akhale mlakatuli. Ichi si china koma chikumbutso ndi dongosolo la Korani
  36,70,Limene lichenjeza anthu a moyo ndi kupereka chiweruzo kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  36,71,Kodi iwo saona kuti pakati pa zinthu zimene tidalenga ndi manja athu tidawalengera nyama zimene iwo amazilamulira
  36,72,Tidalamula zimenezi kuti zizimvera malamulo awo kuti akhoza kumakwera ndi zina zoti azidya
  36,73,Ndipo amapezanso phindu lina lolekana. Iwo amamwa mkaka kuchokera ku izo. Kodi iwo sangathokoze
  36,74,"Iwo akhazikitsa milungu ina powonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, poganiza kuti mwina akhoza kuthandizidwa"
  36,75,Milunguyo siingawathandize. Iwo adzatengedwa mwankhondo kunka ku chilango
  36,76,Usalole kuti mawu awo akumvetse chisoni. Ife tikudziwa zonse zimene azibisa ndi zonse zimene akuzionetsa
  36,77,"Kodi munthu, sadziwa kuti tidamulenga kuchokera ku dontho la umuna? Koma iye ndi otsutsana ndi Ife poyera"
  36,78,"Iye amatifanizira Ife ndi zina zake ndipo amaiwala za chilengedwe chake. Iye amafunsa kuti, “Kodi ndani amene adzapereka moyo ku mafupa oola?”"
  36,79,Nena “Iye amene adawalenga poyamba adzawapatsa moyo. Iye amadziwa chilichonse cha zolengedwa zake.”
  36,80,Iye amene amakupatsani moto kuchokera ku mtengo wauwisi umene inu mumawunikira
  36,81,"Kodi Iye amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, alibe mphamvu zolenga china chake chofanana nazo? Ndithudi ali nazo. Iye ndi Mlengi amene amadziwa chinthu china chilichonse"
  36,82,"Ndithudi pamene Iye afuna chinthu amangonena kuti, “Chikhale” ndipo chimakhaladi"
  36,83,Ulemerero ukhale kwa Iye amene ali ndi ulamuliro pa chinthu china chilichonse; ndipo ndi kwa Iye kumene nonse mudzabwerera
  37,1,Pali iwo amene amasonkhana kukhala pa maudindo osiyanasiyana
  37,2,Pali iwo amene amayendetsa mitambo mwa ubwino
  37,3,Pali iwo amene amabweretsa m’Buku ndi Korani kuchokera kwa Mulungu kupita nalo kwa anthu ake
  37,4,Ndithudi Mulungu wanu ndi mmodzi yekha
  37,5,Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi wa zonse zimene zili m’menemo ndi Ambuye wa dera lililonse lotulukira dzuwa
  37,6,Ndithudi Ife tidakongoletsa mtambo woyandikira kwambiri ndi nyenyezi
  37,7,Ndi kulonda Satana wofukira
  37,8,Kotero iwo sangathe kumvetsera zokambidwa za gulu lapamwamba chifukwa iwo amapirikitsidwa kuchokera kumbali iliyonse
  37,9,"Atapirikitsidwa, chawo chidzakhala chilango chosatha"
  37,10,"Kupatula yekhayo amene amakwatula zinthu mwakuba, ndipo amathamangitsidwa ndi moto woyaka ndi wowala kwambiri"
  37,11,"Ndipo tawafunsa, “Kodi iwo ndi a mphamvu kuposa zolengedwa zina zimene tidalenga?” Iwo tidawalenga kuchokera ku dothi lonyata la makande"
  37,12,"Iyayi, iwe udadabwa pamene iwo anali kunyoza"
  37,13,"Ndipo iwo akamaweruzidwa, iwo safuna kuweruzidwa"
  37,14,Ndipo iwo akaona chizindikiro chochokera kwa Mulungu amachisandutsa ngati chinthu choseweretsa
  37,15,"Ndipo amati, “Ichi si china ayi koma matsenga woonekera poyera.”"
  37,16,"“Chiyani! Ife tikafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, kodi tidzaukitsidwa?”"
  37,17,“Ndiponso makolo athu amakedzana?”
  37,18,"Nena, “Inde mudzachititsidwa manyazi.”"
  37,19,Ndipo udzakhala mfuwu umodzi ndipo taona iwo adzakhala ali kupenyetsetsana
  37,20,"Iwo adzati, “Tsoka kwa ife! Ili ndi tsiku lachiweruzo.”"
  37,21,“Ili ndi tsiku lachiweruzo limene inu mumati ndi bodza.”